{"tid":937464,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"（長文）同女神出街 用左coupon請佢.....","createTime":"2018-12-11T14:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T15:36:06.000Z","uid":135160,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2cd1620c1a4dad63c699e7107ace0ad3ab8e9e45","tid":937464,"uid":135160,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:29:51.000Z","msg":"我識左女神都有3個幾月 平時最多都係傾下電話 WHATSAPP下咁 <br />\n<br />\n最近我終於成功咁約到佢出黎 因為我知女神好鍾意飲咖啡 我見我老母唔知買左邊本雜誌番黎 <br />\n有頁仲送STARBUCKS 既COUPON 大拿拿成廿幾蚊 我就即刻好興奮咁打比女神約佢出黎 <br />\n<br />\n因為平時問老母拎錢 佢叫我唔好買咖啡 成30蚊杯好唔抵 都夠食到個餐 所以我一直都唔敢約女神 <br />\n去到STARBUCKS果陣 女神就話:不如我去搵個位坐住先啦 我驚一陣冇位坐啊 <br />\n<br />\n我:唔洗啦 好快排到我地 (其實我係想留女神係到 一陣用英文點COFFEE 威比佢睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n<br />\n排到我地果陣 我就拎左張COUPON出黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再好有自信而且大聲用英文講: ONE LATTE! BIG SIZE! NO SWEET! (我記得係用緊美國口音) <br />\n女神呆哂係旁邊望住我 就細細聲問:咦..乜你剩係點1杯既...? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我:係囉 本雜誌到比得1張COUPON..所以咪叫得1杯囉..放心啦..我留比你飲架 <br />\n<br />\n我見佢聽到之後個樣都好似幾放心咁 我再用番有自信既眼神望住個STAFF <br />\n佢係我手上面拎左張COUPON之後 望左2望 就話:FREE <br />\n喱個時候我就唔耐煩 係人都知有COUPON就FREE架啦 我就串柒柒咁話: I KNOW <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後我就拉住女神去搵位 點知我一轉身果陣 佢就話: HEY SIR ..THREE DOLLARS PLEASE <br />\n女神都忍唔住笑左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我拎番張野睇睇 原來我叫最大果個SIZE都仲要加錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我未黎過唔知 <br />\n<br />\n我為左保住面子 我就話:好心啦..香港人就咪學人講英文啦..一早講廣東話我咪明囉.. <br />\n佢:係囉 但你記得分清楚FREE同THREE啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後去拎咖啡我都唔敢幫女神去拎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女神仲暗串我冇風度 唉 今次既約會真係好失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99393c63f02c4e627e244a8f77f29d25af2b7798","tid":937464,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:32:57.000Z","msg":"樓豬好man<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />睇到我扯晒旗啦！！！！"},{"pid":"ca094e8e805c9d05a99abc7240dafead6ef136a7","tid":937464,"uid":138138,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1ze3y3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1ze3y3.jpg&h=3d74ff6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"371c8d0e24c8182a22571805e9c697155b342d31","tid":937464,"uid":135160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca094e8e805c9d05a99abc7240dafead6ef136a7","tid":937464,"uid":138138,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1ze3y3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1ze3y3.jpg&h=3d74ff6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> no gay"},{"pid":"6679ab1200c112d55eef615bcdde4b6c21a7a65d","tid":937464,"uid":135160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 已經好唔開心..."},{"pid":"1ca3236df3ee4d3b40845a7d25124534bb1f3db5","tid":937464,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"371c8d0e24c8182a22571805e9c697155b342d31","tid":937464,"uid":135160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca094e8e805c9d05a99abc7240dafead6ef136a7","tid":937464,"uid":138138,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y1ze3y3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY1ze3y3.jpg&h=3d74ff6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T14:34:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> no gay"},"citedBy":1,"rep